 in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.017402, "shard": "02", "shelf_id": "sn89051213, 1907-11-28, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/arhi", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["mena", "arkansas", "https://id.oclc.org/worldcat/entity/e39pbjtcyhcxdxqhdtjcqvkkh3", "united states", "newspapers", "mena (ark.)", "polk"], "subject_headings": ["Mena (Ark.)--Newspapers", "Arkansas--Mena.--https://id.oclc.org/worldcat/entity/E39PBJtCyHCxdXQhDTJcQvKKh3", "United States--Arkansas--Polk--Mena"], "subjects": [{"arkansas": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:arkansas&fo=json"}, {"https://id.oclc.org/worldcat/entity/e39pbjtcyhcxdxqhdtjcqvkkh3": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:https://id.oclc.org/worldcat/entity/e39pbjtcyhcxdxqhdtjcqvkkh3&fo=json"}, {"mena": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:mena&fo=json"}, {"mena (ark.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:mena+%28ark.%29&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"polk": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:polk&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2024-12-03T15:07:10.803Z", "title": "The Mena weekly star (Mena, Ark.), November 28, 1907", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn89051213/1907-11-28/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn89051213/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn89051213", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/80fc2b89-c9bc-5dd4-b5cb-c42e319f2d11"], "batch": ["arhi_igglybuff_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1904", "description": ["Weekly Vol. 21, no. 37 (Sept. 8, 1904)-v. 94, no. 43 (Oct. 27, 1977). Beginning Nov. 1977, the Mena evening star was issued once a week with title: Mena star, and mailed as a weekly. Published as: Mena weekly star and the Polk County Democrat, Jan. 6-July 6, 1916. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Absorbed: Polk County Democrat, and: Democrat (Mena, Ark.) (non-extant)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:10.056Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-14", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-14"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn89051213/", "image_url": [], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [34.5830759, -94.2353904], "location": ["united states", "arkansas", "polk", "mena"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-94.2353904, 34.5830759], "number": ["original", "19739258", "sn85032997", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "680", "kansas state hist soc, newsp proj", "2693-0064", "sn89051213", "southwest arkansas regional library", "2024-03-06t16:54:13.143771", "microfilm master", "online resource", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn89051213/1922-03-23/ed-1/", "arkansas hist comn", "2025-07-01t13:40:53.300000